      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>EHRENPREIS-Pearl. On August 19, 2000. Loving wife of Walter. Devoted mother of Susan and Sandra. Proud grandmother of Ariel. Beloved sister of Murray, George, Irving and Sy. Adored teacher for 37 years. She will always be in our hearts and minds. A memorial service will be held at Sinai Chapels in Fresh Meadows on Monday, August 21, at 1:45 PM.</p>
      </block>
